comments: Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Wright (MEM) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Parsons (MEM) makes contact to Parker's (WAS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Parsons (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Satoransky (WAS) and slightly extends his arm against his side but he is able to move through contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Satoransky (WAS) and makes some contact to his front during the pick but he is able to defend through the play.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact with Valanciunas (MEM) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Valanciunas (MEM) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) arm but he is able to move through contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) briefly grasps Bryant's (WAS) arm but does not affect his ability to move.
[Observable in enhanced video] Conley (MEM) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Satoransky (WAS) and gives him room to avoid contact.
LAR shows Bryant (WAS) makes marginal contact with Conley (MEM) during his driving shot attempt.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bradley (MEM) and slightly extends his arm against Bradley (MEM) during the pick but he is able to move through contact.
Noah (MEM) briefly grasps Bryant's (WAS) arm during the pick but does not affect his FOM.
LLB shows Noah (MEM) places a hand/arm to the front of Beal (WAS) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beal (WAS) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Conley (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beal (WAS) and firms up during the screen but is able to move through contact.
Satoransky (WAS) briefly grasps Bradley's (MEM) arm during the screen but does not affect his FOM.
Valanciunas (MEM) engages with Bryant (WAS) prior to the pick but he is able to move through contact.
LLB shows Conley (MEM) makes hand on ball contact during Beal's (WAS) shot attempt. Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Satoransky (WAS) and firms up on his side during the pick but he is able to move through contact.
Beal (WAS) makes contact with the ball and marginal contact with Bradley's (MEM) arm.
Parker (WAS) places a hand/arm to the front of Conley (MEM) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Conley (MEM) grasps Satoransky's (WAS) arm but does not affect his FOM.
Holiday (MEM) commits a clear path foul on Parker (MEM).
Wright (MEM) commits a take foul on Satoransky (WAS).
